    "It is worth stating that TM techniques were applied in these domains in various ways.",
    "For illustration, in cases of online forums, social media, review, feedback, and survey dataset, TM were applied for topic extraction or theme discovery.",
    "More specifically, in tourism and hospitality context, popular datasets were collected from reviews (Yelp, Trivago, Tripadvisor, Trustpilot, Travelpod, booking.com, IgoUgo, PegiPegi), feedback, customer survey, social media, online forums and discussion.",
    "Thereafter, TM were applied to mine customer information on service experience, satisfaction or quality.",
